{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/network/2","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"97e362c7-0012-5e76-8349-969e4594acae","html":"<h3 id=\"dns\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dns\" aria-label=\"dns permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DNS</h3>\n<p>도메인 네임 서비스는 기억하기 힘든 서버의 주소에 이름을 부여해 매핑해주는 서버이다.</p>\n<p>dns에 주소 요청</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">➜  ~ <span class=\"token function\">nslookup</span> www.naver.com\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> Got recursion not available from <span class=\"token number\">211.252</span>.120.62, trying next server\nServer:\t\t<span class=\"token number\">168.126</span>.63.1\nAddress:\t<span class=\"token number\">168.126</span>.63.1<span class=\"token comment\">#53</span>\n\nNon-authoritative answer:\nwww.naver.com\tcanonical name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> www.naver.com.nheos.com.\nName:\twww.naver.com.nheos.com\nAddress: <span class=\"token number\">223.130</span>.195.200\nName:\twww.naver.com.nheos.com\nAddress: <span class=\"token number\">125.209</span>.222.142</code></pre></div>\n<p>위의 예처럼 dns에 처음에 요청을 넣고 이에 반환값을 통해 우리가 원하는 서버에 접속을 합니다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"dns의-종류\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dns%EC%9D%98-%EC%A2%85%EB%A5%98\" aria-label=\"dns의 종류 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DNS의 종류</h4>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b5470bc7f9c22627c3652ab565b89b9c/387f2/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 88.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/b5470bc7f9c22627c3652ab565b89b9c/8ac56/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8.webp 240w,\n/static/b5470bc7f9c22627c3652ab565b89b9c/d3be9/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8.webp 480w,\n/static/b5470bc7f9c22627c3652ab565b89b9c/e46b2/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8.webp 960w,\n/static/b5470bc7f9c22627c3652ab565b89b9c/f992d/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8.webp 1440w,\n/static/b5470bc7f9c22627c3652ab565b89b9c/ebc20/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8.webp 1518w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/b5470bc7f9c22627c3652ab565b89b9c/8ff5a/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8.png 240w,\n/static/b5470bc7f9c22627c3652ab565b89b9c/e85cb/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8.png 480w,\n/static/b5470bc7f9c22627c3652ab565b89b9c/d9199/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8.png 960w,\n/static/b5470bc7f9c22627c3652ab565b89b9c/07a9c/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8.png 1440w,\n/static/b5470bc7f9c22627c3652ab565b89b9c/387f2/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8.png 1518w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/b5470bc7f9c22627c3652ab565b89b9c/d9199/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8.png\"\n          alt=\"dns서버리스트\"\n          title=\"dns서버리스트\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>운영체제별로 dns설정을 할 수 있는 세팅기능이 있는데 위의 dns서버리스트중 하나로 세팅되어있는듯 합니다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.codns.com/b/B05-170\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">이미지 출처</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"dns-서버의-역할-3가지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dns-%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EC%9D%98-%EC%97%AD%ED%95%A0-3%EA%B0%80%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"dns 서버의 역할 3가지 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DNS 서버의 역할 3가지</h4>\n<p>도메인 네임과 호스트 네임</p>\n<ul>\n<li>도메인네임 : 해당 서버ip 자체를 대표 이름</li>\n<li>호스트네임(서브도메인) : 해당 서버의 서브 서비스별로 가진 서브 도메인들에대한 이름</li>\n<li>\n<p>예시 (naver)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>도메인 네임 : naver.com</li>\n<li>호스트 네임 : www.naver.com, cafe.naver.com, mybox.naver.com 등등</li>\n<li>처음 알았는데 www.naver.com과 naver.com은 분리가 가능합니다. naver를 예로 naver.com은 네이버의 모든 호스트네임에대한 대표 같은 정보이고 도메인네임으로 접속시 main페이지인 www.naver.com로 리다이렉트 되는것 같습니다. 이후 cafe나 mybox등등 이있는데 앞에 www.을 붙이면 연결되지 않습니다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"호스트-엘리어싱host-aliasing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%98%B8%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8-%EC%97%98%EB%A6%AC%EC%96%B4%EC%8B%B1host-aliasing\" aria-label=\"호스트 엘리어싱host aliasing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>호스트 엘리어싱(host aliasing)</h5>\n<p>호스트 네임은 하나이상의 별칭을 가질 수 있으며 호스트 네임보다 별칭이 더 기억하기 좋다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">➜  ~ <span class=\"token function\">nslookup</span> -queyr<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>cname www.naver.com\n*** Invalid option: <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">queyr</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>cname\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> Got recursion not available from <span class=\"token number\">211.252</span>.120.62, trying next server\nServer:\t\t<span class=\"token number\">168.126</span>.63.1\nAddress:\t<span class=\"token number\">168.126</span>.63.1<span class=\"token comment\">#53</span>\n\nNon-authoritative answer:\nwww.naver.com\tcanonical name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> www.naver.com.nheos.com.\nName:\twww.naver.com.nheos.com\nAddress: <span class=\"token number\">125.209</span>.222.141\nName:\twww.naver.com.nheos.com\nAddress: <span class=\"token number\">125.209</span>.222.142</code></pre></div>\n<p>네이버 메인페이지의 정식 호스트 이름은 www.naver.com.nheos.com입니다.</p>\n<p>아래 블로그글이 사용예시로써 이해하기 좋았습니다.\n<a href=\"https://thebook.io/007046/ch07/02/05/03/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">cname의 사용 예</a></p>\n<h5 id=\"메일-엘리어싱\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%BC-%EC%97%98%EB%A6%AC%EC%96%B4%EC%8B%B1\" aria-label=\"메일 엘리어싱 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>메일 엘리어싱</h5>\n<p>기업의 메일서버와 웹 서버가 동일한 호스트 네임(별칭)을 가지도록 허용해 줍니다.</p>\n<h5 id=\"부하-분산\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B6%80%ED%95%98-%EB%B6%84%EC%82%B0\" aria-label=\"부하 분산 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>부하 분산</h5>\n<p>여러 개의 IP주소가 정식 호스트네임과 연관되도록 설정할 수 있다.\nDNS에 질의를 하면 등록된 여러개의 IP를 순환해 반환한다. nslookup으로 조회시 도메인네임 또는 호스트네임마다 여러가지 ip가 출력되는 경우가 있는데 그만큼 서버가 여러대로 운영되고 있으며 한쪽에 몰리지 않고 분산시켜 부하를 분산 시켜준다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"dns-동작원리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dns-%EB%8F%99%EC%9E%91%EC%9B%90%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"dns 동작원리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DNS 동작원리</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>UDP(53번 포트) 프로토콜를 사용 : DNS는 인터넷을 사용하는 모든 사용자가 사용하는 서버임으로 트래픽이 많고 빠르 속도를 지원해야 합니다. 요청에대한 쿼리양이 많아지면 TCP를 사용하기도 합니다.</li>\n<li>분산된 계층 데이터베이스로 구성\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eb4a82ddb240e0da750cff4fcdcdef9e/ae28e/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dnsDB.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/eb4a82ddb240e0da750cff4fcdcdef9e/8ac56/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dnsDB.webp 240w,\n/static/eb4a82ddb240e0da750cff4fcdcdef9e/d3be9/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dnsDB.webp 480w,\n/static/eb4a82ddb240e0da750cff4fcdcdef9e/e46b2/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dnsDB.webp 960w,\n/static/eb4a82ddb240e0da750cff4fcdcdef9e/f992d/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dnsDB.webp 1440w,\n/static/eb4a82ddb240e0da750cff4fcdcdef9e/2eb6a/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dnsDB.webp 1598w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/eb4a82ddb240e0da750cff4fcdcdef9e/8ff5a/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dnsDB.png 240w,\n/static/eb4a82ddb240e0da750cff4fcdcdef9e/e85cb/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dnsDB.png 480w,\n/static/eb4a82ddb240e0da750cff4fcdcdef9e/d9199/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dnsDB.png 960w,\n/static/eb4a82ddb240e0da750cff4fcdcdef9e/07a9c/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dnsDB.png 1440w,\n/static/eb4a82ddb240e0da750cff4fcdcdef9e/ae28e/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dnsDB.png 1598w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/eb4a82ddb240e0da750cff4fcdcdef9e/d9199/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dnsDB.png\"\n          alt=\"dns-DB\"\n          title=\"dns-DB\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>로컬 DNS 서버 : 우리나라를 예로 SKT, KT, LG에서 제공하는 DNS를 말합니다. ISP에서 DNS를 운영해 제공하며 DNS 방식중 하나이므로 어떤게 더 빠를지 생각해보고 사용하면 될듯 합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"dns-캐싱\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dns-%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1\" aria-label=\"dns 캐싱 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DNS 캐싱</h4>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1365e94e026cb559251de5f5726c5272/e2d3b/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.24999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/1365e94e026cb559251de5f5726c5272/8ac56/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1.webp 240w,\n/static/1365e94e026cb559251de5f5726c5272/d3be9/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1.webp 480w,\n/static/1365e94e026cb559251de5f5726c5272/e46b2/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1.webp 960w,\n/static/1365e94e026cb559251de5f5726c5272/f992d/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1.webp 1440w,\n/static/1365e94e026cb559251de5f5726c5272/00ee8/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1.webp 1466w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/1365e94e026cb559251de5f5726c5272/8ff5a/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1.png 240w,\n/static/1365e94e026cb559251de5f5726c5272/e85cb/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1.png 480w,\n/static/1365e94e026cb559251de5f5726c5272/d9199/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1.png 960w,\n/static/1365e94e026cb559251de5f5726c5272/07a9c/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1.png 1440w,\n/static/1365e94e026cb559251de5f5726c5272/e2d3b/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1.png 1466w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/1365e94e026cb559251de5f5726c5272/d9199/5%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8-dns%EC%BA%90%EC%8B%B1.png\"\n          alt=\"DNS_캐싱\"\n          title=\"DNS_캐싱\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n자주 사용되는 도메인을 DNS에서 보관해두는 것</p>\n<h4 id=\"dns-레코드와-메시지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dns-%EB%A0%88%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C%EC%99%80-%EB%A9%94%EC%8B%9C%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"dns 레코드와 메시지 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DNS 레코드와 메시지</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>자원 레코드 형식</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Name : 상직적 이름</li>\n<li>Type : 유형</li>\n<li>Value : 타입에 따른 값을 부여</li>\n<li>TTL : dns 캐싱 정보의 유지시간</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Type 별 레코드 예시</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Type=A(1) : 호스트의 ip 주소 매핑</li>\n<li>Name : 호스트 이름</li>\n<li>Value : IPv4 주소(IPv6는 따로인가…?)</li>\n<li>Type=NS(2) : 주어진 호스트에 대한 공식적인 이름 서버를 알려줌</li>\n<li>Name : 도메인 이름</li>\n<li>Value : 네임서버의 호스트 이름</li>\n<li>Type=CNAME(5) : 소유한 도메인에 별칭을 지정</li>\n<li>Name : 별칭 호스트네임</li>\n<li>Value : 정식 호스트네임</li>\n<li>Type=MX(15) : 메일에대한 별칭을 저장, 메일 수신서버 지정</li>\n<li>Name : 메일서버 별칭</li>\n<li>Value : 호스트 이름</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/network/2","tagSlugs":["/tag/dns/","/tag/network/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-05-16T00:00:00","description":"dns를 공부해 보았습니다.","tags":["DNS","network"],"title":"DNS(도메인네임,호스트네임 등등)","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/624cc4a835e68430a8beec01cef8ac6c/photo.jpg"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/network/2"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}